  "Description": {
    "English": "The Icarus system takes advantage of existing metal panelling, upgrading them into photovoltaic surfaces. This reactive coating generates energy during daylight hours, offsetting fuel consumption.<br><br>Enables <span class=\"name name-stellar\">automatic engine recharging</span> during the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">day</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "伊卡勒斯系统会利用现有的金属面板，将其升级为光伏表面。这种活性涂层会在日光下产生能量，用于补偿燃料消耗。<br><br>启用<span class=\"name name-stellar\">白天</span>时<span class=\"name name-stellar\">自动引擎充能</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "伊卡洛斯系統利用了現有的金屬嵌版，並升級為光電表層。此活性塗層會在日照時間生成能量，抵銷燃料耗損。<br><br>能在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">日間</span>開啟<span class=\"name name-stellar\">自動引擎充能</span>。"
  },
